@Component
script UI_SimpleTooltipActivator extends Component

	@Description("제목/설명만으로 이뤄진 심플한 툴팁을 활성화시킬 때 사용하는 컴포넌트입니다.")
	@DisplayName("READ ME")
	property boolean ReadMe = false

	property string Title = ""

	property string Desc = ""

	property Entity UI_Tooltip = "01fc22d7-fcb5-4ba5-a698-3ef57411f706"

	property Entity UI_Tooltip_Title = "fa840b39-c1bd-47fc-8fd6-f24726e8b978"

	property Entity UI_Tooltip_Desc = "96a7fde3-23b0-4e06-ae2b-bf4873dd99e1"

	@ExecSpace("ClientOnly")
	@EventSender("Self")
	handler HandleUITouchEnterEvent(UITouchEnterEvent event)
		-- 마우스 호버 시 툴팁 표시
		-- Parameters
		-- local Entity = event.Entity
		-- local TouchId = event.TouchId
		-- local TouchPoint = event.TouchPoint
		---------------------------------------------------------
		self.UI_Tooltip_Title.TextComponent.Text = _LocalizationService:GetText(self.Title)
		self.UI_Tooltip_Desc.TextComponent.Text = _LocalizationService:GetText(self.Desc)
		self.UI_Tooltip.Enable = true
	end

	@ExecSpace("ClientOnly")
	@EventSender("Self")
	handler HandleUITouchExitEvent(UITouchExitEvent event)
		-- 마우스 호버 해제 시 툴팁 숨김
		-- Parameters
		-- local Entity = event.Entity
		-- local TouchId = event.TouchId
		-- local TouchPoint = event.TouchPoint
		---------------------------------------------------------
		self.UI_Tooltip.Enable = false
	end

end